00:48.920 --> 00:50.920
♪ Thursday, Friday, happy days ♪

00:50.920 --> 00:53.920
♪ Saturday, what a day ♪

00:53.920 --> 00:56.420
♪ Groovin' all week with you ♪

00:56.420 --> 00:57.920
♪ These days are ours ♪

