17:13.900 --> 17:15.869
Yeah, well, you're
young, you'll recover.

17:16.119 --> 17:17.700
(whimpers)

17:18.200 --> 17:19.710
(girls shrieking, squealing)

17:20.210 --> 17:22.710
And you think
<i><font size="24"><font face="Arial">you've got a problem{\r}.</font></font></i>

17:27.210 --> 17:28.660
Come on, Malph,

17:29.080 --> 17:31.670
