for an examination--

19:18.770 --> 19:20.280
I got to get back to work.

19:20.780 --> 19:21.660
Listen, I, uh,

19:21.940 --> 19:24.360
I came here to talk
to you about Ralph.

19:24.610 --> 19:26.030
He won!

19:26.280 --> 19:28.370
My little Ralphie--
he's Leopard of the Year!

19:28.370 --> 19:29.870
Oh-ho, sit back, sit back!

19:29.870 --> 19:31.870
